<svg viewBox="0 0 700 800" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
  <text x="20" y="28" fill="#fafafa" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="16" font-weight="700">Price Is at a 3-Week High, Conviction Isn't There Yet</text>
  <text x="20" y="48" fill="#a1a1aa" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="13">Checking funding rate, ETF flows, and Fear &amp; Greed as of Jul 16</text>
  <rect x="20" y="66" width="660" height="100" rx="10" fill="#18181b" stroke="#3f3f46"/>
  <text x="40" y="92" fill="#a1a1aa" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="13">Price: $62,259 (Jul 14 open) → $64,988 (Jul 14 intraday high)</text>
  <text x="40" y="120" fill="#34d399" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="22" font-weight="800">+12% (vs Jun 30 low)</text>
  <text x="270" y="120" fill="#71717a" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="13">$64,800-$65,300 on Jul 16 afternoon, 3-week high</text>
  <text x="40" y="148" fill="#71717a" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="13">June CPI −0.4% (biggest drop in 4 yrs) · Core 0.0% (vs +0.2% exp.)</text>
  <text x="20" y="192" fill="#d4d4d8" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" font-weight="700">Derivatives: Funding Rate</text>
